{%- comment -%}
  ============================================================================
  worker-trust · widget "Confianza" (badges + mensajes)  (shopify-control · F2)
  ============================================================================
  Bloque Custom Liquid. Se pega UNA vez, desde el editor de temas, en la
  plantilla de producto, CERCA del botón "Agregar al carrito". NO se edita
  ningún archivo del tema.

  Lee product.metafields.worker.trust y, si no hay, cae a shop.metafields.worker.trust
  (un badge puede ser por producto o de toda la tienda). Renderiza los ítems de
  tipo `badge` y `message`. Los ítems `whatsapp` los ignora acá: los muestra el
  bloque flotante worker-whatsapp.liquid. Si no hay ítems inline, no renderiza nada.

  El texto va server-rendered (crawleable + `| escape`); los íconos son un set
  cerrado de SVG (nunca URLs ni SVG del usuario → sin inyección).

  Diseño: docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-22-pack-latam-vitrina-design.md §6
  Guard:  worker.trust validado por COSMETIC_METAFIELDS en backup_guard.py
  ============================================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign trust = product.metafields.worker.trust.value | default: shop.metafields.worker.trust.value -%}
{%- if trust and trust.items and trust.items.size > 0 -%}
{%- assign has_inline = false -%}
{%- for it in trust.items -%}{%- if it.type == "badge" or it.type == "message" -%}{%- assign has_inline = true -%}{%- endif -%}{%- endfor -%}
{%- if has_inline -%}

<div id="worker-trust" class="wt">
  {%- for it in trust.items -%}
    {%- if it.type == "badge" -%}
    <span class="wt-badge">
      <span class="wt-ico" aria-hidden="true">{%- case it.icon -%}
        {%- when "cuotas" -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M2 10h20"/></svg>
        {%- when "transferencia" -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 7h15l-3-3M20 17H5l3 3"/></svg>
        {%- when "envio" -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 5h11v10H2zM13 8h4l4 4v3h-8"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="1.6"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="18" r="1.6"/></svg>
        {%- when "garantia" -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3l7 3v5c0 4-3 7-7 8-4-1-7-4-7-8V6z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        {%- when "seguridad" -%}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="5" y="11" width="14" height="9" rx="2"/><path d="M8 11V7a4 4 0 018 0v4"/></svg>
      {%- endcase -%}</span>
      <span class="wt-txt">{{ it.text | escape }}</span>
    </span>
    {%- elsif it.type == "message" -%}
    <p class="wt-msg">{{ it.text | escape }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>

<style>
  #worker-trust.wt{
    --wt-ink:#4B4B4B; --wt-sage:#9CB0B1; --wt-line:rgba(75,75,75,.18);
    font-family:inherit; color:var(--wt-ink); margin:14px 0; max-width:520px;
    display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px 10px; align-items:center;
  }
  #worker-trust .wt-badge{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; padding:6px 11px;
    border:1.5px solid var(--wt-line); border-radius:20px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600;
  }
  #worker-trust .wt-ico{ display:inline-flex; color:var(--wt-sage); }
  #worker-trust .wt-msg{
    flex-basis:100%; margin:2px 0 0; font-size:12.5px; opacity:.75;
  }
</style>
{%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
